Question: Assume generator class consists of three 8-bit data members (x,y, and z). Write a code to generate 20 random values for all the data members at an interval of 20 ns.


class sample;

rand bit[7:0] x;
rand bit[7:0] y;
rand bit[7:0] z;

endclass



module tb;

sample s = new();

initial begin

repeat(20) begin

assert(s.randomize()) else $display("Randomization Failed!!") ;

  $display("x = %d  | y = %d  | z = %d  | time %0t",s.x,s.y,s.z,$time);

  #20;

end

end

endmodule
